'''凱斯·羅伯特·桑斯坦'''（{{Lang-en|'''Cass Robert Sunstein'''}}，或譯'''桑思汀'''<ref name=":0">{{Cite news|url=https://theinitium.com/article/20151228-opinion-sunstein/|title=專訪桑思汀：分歧之下如何保障選擇與自由|accessdate=2017-03-01|archive-date=2017-03-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170301182141/https://theinitium.com/article/20151228-opinion-sunstein/|dead-url=no}}</ref>，{{Bd|1954年|9月21日}}）<ref name="bork1">{{cite book|url=https://books.google.com/?id=EWERAQAAMAAJ&q=Marian+(Goodrich)+Sunstein&dq=Marian+(Goodrich)+Sunstein|title=Current biography yearbook – H.W. Wilson Company – Google Books|publisher=Books.google.ca|accessdate=2012-07-27|year=2008}}</ref>，[[美國|美國]][[法學者|法律學者]]，他的專業領域為[[憲法|憲法]]、[[行政法|行政法]]、[[环境法学|環境法]]以及法律經濟行為。

==生平==
他曾在2009年至2012年之間擔任歐巴馬政府的白宮資訊及管制事務辦公室主任<ref>[https://www.nytimes.com/2013/04/09/books/simpler-and-simple.html ''Be Fruitful and Simplify!  ‘Simpler’ and ‘Simple’''] {{Wayback|url=https://www.nytimes.com/2013/04/09/books/simpler-and-simple.html |date=20170301184429 }} April 8, 2013 New York Times</ref>，並曾任教於[[芝加哥大学法学院|芝加哥大學法學院]]達27年之久；現在，桑斯坦為[[哈佛法学院|哈佛法學院]]的羅伯特·沃姆斯利[[講座教授|講座教授]]<ref>{{cite web|url=http://news.harvard.edu/gazette/story/2013/02/sunstein-a-university-professor/|title=Sunstein a University Professor|work=Harvard Gazette|accessdate=2017-03-01|archive-date=2017-03-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170321015448/http://news.harvard.edu/gazette/story/2013/02/sunstein-a-university-professor/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。<ref>[http://www.leiterrankings.com/faculty/2014_scholarlyimpact.shtml 2014 Scholarly Impact – Leitner Rankings] {{Wayback|url=http://www.leiterrankings.com/faculty/2014_scholarlyimpact.shtml |date=20170318013922 }}.</ref><ref>{{Cite journal|title=Judicial Impact of Law School Faculties|url=http://papers.ssrn.com/abstract=2832981|last=Farris|first=Nick|last2=Aggerbeck|first2=Valerie|date=2016-08-18|publisher=Social Science Research Network|doi=10.2139/ssrn.2826048|location=Rochester, NY|last3=McNevin|first3=Megan|last4=Sisk|first4=Gregory C.}}</ref><ref name=":0" />

